start.name: Navigator:
start.content: Oh hey, White Dwarf! Good morning!

start.name: Navigator:
start.content: Then... is there something you need?

start.name: Navigator:
start.content: Huh? Then... did you just want to remind me to eat lunch?

start.name: White Dwarf:
start.content: I wanted to... practice social interactions with you, Navigator...

start.name: White Dwarf:
start.content: Did I... say something wrong just now...?

start.name: Navigator:
start.content: I'm touched that you are concerned about me.

start.name: White Dwarf:
start.content: Then can I... still contact you in the future?
